{"tid":876904,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【白眼佘詩曼？】鄧萃雯微笑：我散光喎！有人白眼我都唔知啦","createTime":"2018-10-26T03:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T14:56:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"83bc807af281402ac5310c2936696989bdc6cffc","tid":876904,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"佘詩曼最近接受《魯豫有約一日行》訪問，講起一件往事。一年台慶，阿佘同佢個對手一齊企，等開場。阿佘聲稱當時佢見到前面發生咗一樣好好笑嘅嘢，於是佢就擰轉頭同佢對手講：「嘩，你睇！」但對手完全唔理佢，直頭當阿佘透明一樣，木然不動。<br />\n鏡頭前嘅阿佘，做番當日嗰位對手嘅「木臉」表情，阿佘話當時都忍唔住睥（純眼神交代）咗對方一眼&hellip;&hellip;魯豫問阿佘究竟對手當時係故意唔理佢、定係緊張到冇暇顧及其他？阿佘話：「我不知道。」<br />\n照推測，有幾位花旦機會都幾高，分別係鄧萃雯、張可頤，同黎姿。當年佢哋《金枝慾孽》鬥戲鬥風頭，到今日仲有故仔講。<br />\n雯女今晚到灣仔出席頒獎禮，受訪時被傳媒追問佢是否就係嗰個「白眼對手」，雯女笑：「係咩？我散光0架喎！就算有人白眼我，我都唔知。」亦否認係白眼／無視阿佘嗰位女演員。<br />\n那平時同雯女有冇偈傾？「其實我哋係學姐學妹嚟0架，因為我哋係協恩嘅校友，有時都會同我聯絡，講有關學校嘅嘢，早前有個老師想搵我，阿佘都有同我講。」即係冇不和？雯女笑言：「梗係唔會（不和）啦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540474010_8914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540474010_8914.jpg&h=7be2d60f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"473600030b4872a15c2ef17a198afb5347efa1db","tid":876904,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"有片睇<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181025/58836464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58836464&d=XqyKGnwltAFEwUjO9KPbjl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=74c40b8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58836464&h=9b011a6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181025/58836464</a>"},{"pid":"66adb7c57d8fe6fbd36aa4276dbace5179432a92","tid":876904,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:16:06.000Z","msg":"好想佢兩個用佢哋粉紅嘅腳板底踩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0c46155a39131c6f9fc33abd582d745eede4d4","tid":876904,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"賴C黛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9663bd0eedf502bb343898c683e152e785659c4","tid":876904,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"911e8092789b4dfe69c9354d94ebe16db6bca7f4","tid":876904,"uid":79355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"咸豐年前既野都拎番黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8de092c061b8dc183d782a0cf24ecb667b20c4c","tid":876904,"uid":174654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f0c46155a39131c6f9fc33abd582d745eede4d4","tid":876904,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"賴C黛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"賴絲黛 呢個食唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20abf124d2cdf3abfcfe5fca3ce6bc39159767b5","tid":876904,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"邊度有否認<br />\n淨係會講學校野，姐係平時都冇交流啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}